title: [SOLVED]802-00138 Liquid Damage
message:
Hi. I have a 2015 A1398 820-00138 with liquid damage & no power.

G3hot - .7
pp 3v42 - Good

G3hot Ohms to ground - starts at .7 to .4
CPU is warm 
Liquid damage was around U7200

Any thoughts? Thanks in advance.

title: [SOLVED]802-00138 Liquid Damage
message: That seems like a short from PPBUS to CPU Vcore. If PPBUS is low voltage and CPU is getting warm then the CPU has already died.

title: [SOLVED]802-00138 Liquid Damage
message: Is there any other way to confirm that this board is a lost cause? Thanks in advance.

title: [SOLVED]802-00138 Liquid Damage
message: Resistance between PPBUS_G3H and CPU Vcore coil??

title: [SOLVED]802-00138 Liquid Damage
message: The CPU is heating up while PPBUS is low. Yeah this board is 95% dead.
